  VALUES
    ('1957 Ferrari 250 Testa Rossa','$39.8 million', 'https://w0.peakpx.com/wallpaper/177/536/HD-wallpaper-ferrari-250-testa-rossa-ferrari-tr-24-hours-of-le-mans-retro-racing-car-classic-sports-cars-ferrari.jpg','The 1957 Ferrari 250 Testa Rossa is one of just 34 models ever built, said Shibarshin. Along with racing around the world and gathering numerous wins, the car was known for its impeccable styling. Today, the Testa Rossa is worth tens of millions. In fact, an unrestored 250 Testa Rossa traded hands in 2014 for nearly $40 million, according to AutoBlog.','2021-05-07 18:57:42.517205-07');